  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b8e\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 ! 3 \u0bb5\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd 9000 \u0b9f\u0bc6\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0bcb\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Warning people! 9000 Dengue patients in 3 weeks",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "The prevalence of dengue is increasing rapidly in the country. About 9000 dengue cases have been identified within last 3 weeks.",
        "Director of the National Dengue Eradication Unit, Special Medical Specialist Sudath Samaraweera said that the dengue eradication measures should be intensified before the situation reaches extreme levels.",
        "About 9000 dengue cases have been identified in the last 3 weeks. This situation should be controlled immediately to prevent dengue from becoming a serious disease.",
        "For this, it is essential to identify the places where dengue fever can multiply and keep them clean and also to keep clean the surrounding environment where the houses and places of business are located.",
        "(25) Monday was declared National Dengue Eradication Day. An hour was set aside in all government and private institutions and dengue eradication work was carried out.",
        "The National Dengue Eradication Unit has reported that 44,000 dengue patients have been identified in the period so far this year, i.e. in about 7 months.",
        "He said that as the rate of spreading of dengue disease is increasing in the country, we urge you not to ignore the symptoms of dengue disease and to go to the hospital immediately for treatment."
      ],
